{
  "texts": [
    "We measure the performance using a variety of captioning metrics.",
    "Following Forbes et al. [11], we report the scores on ROUGE-L [26], CIDEr [46] and BLEU-4 [37].Baselines.",
    "For a comprehensive comparison, we consider opensource state-of-the-art MLLMs including MiniGPT-4 [52], LLaVA [29], BLIP2 [23], InstructBLIP [9], Otter [21], Cheetah [24] and MMICL [51], as well as industrial multi-modal chatbots including GPT-4V [35] and Gemini Pro [2].",
    "Please refer to supplementary Section 3 for detailed experimental settings and Section 4 for more experimental results.",
    "Performance ComparisonThe overall results of SAM and baselines are listed in Table 2."
  ]
}